
How to remove jenkins from Ubuntu ?

sudo service jenkins stop
sudo apt-get remove --purge jenkins
sudo apt-get remove --auto-remove jenkins


How to remove java from Ubuntu ?
sudo rm -rf /usr/lib/jvm/*
sudo apt install openjdk-8-jre-headless --reinstall


How to remove git from Ubuntu ?
sudo apt-get purge --auto-remove gi

How to remove open jdk from Ubuntu ?
sudo rm -rf /usr/lib/jvm/*
 

Softwares Installation steps for Jenkins 
----------------------------------------

1) Java 
2) Maven
3) Git
4) Jenkins

Java Steps
----------
apt search openjdk
sudo apt install openjdk-8-jdk
java -version 

Maven
-----
sudo apt install maven

Git
---
sudo apt install git

Jenkins
-------


lsb_release -a
it will give information about your OS informatin & CodeName 

apt policy jenkins
glen@Xen2:~$ apt policy daemon





